cs.AR, cs.CV, cs.SY, cs.ET, cs.NE 

This paper discusses the mapping of Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) on FPGAs, which falls under the categories of computer architecture (cs.AR), computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV), and systems and control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper discusses the challenges and objectives introduced by the latest trends in CNN algorithmic research, which could also fall under the categories of emerging technologies (cs.ET) and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
